@NODE "Latest" "AmigaTalk latest additions:"

   For Version 2.7, the following enhancements/bug fixes were
   made:

   * The archive now contains a reset AmigaTalk.env file.  The first
     time you run AmigaTalk it will ask you for a ScreenModeID to
     use, then save it in AmigaTalk.env when the program exits.
      
   * The Install script no longer dies due to lack of Hooks/ or
     CodeLib/.  The install script has been verified to work 
     correctly with V2.7.
     
   * Menu checking now agrees with command line paramters.
              
@ENDNODE

